Objects such as <link=\"URANIUMORE\">Uranium Ore</link> and <link=\"BEE\">Beeta Hives</link> emit a <link=\"RADIOACTIVE\">Radioactive</link> energy that can be toxic to my Duplicants.\n\nI can use the <b>Radiation Overlay</b> {Hotkey/Overlay15} to check the scope of the Radiation field. Building thick walls around radiation emitters will dampen the field and protect my Duplicants from getting <link=\"RADIATIONSICKNESS\">Radiation Sickness</link>.